header.gameNote: NEW YORK LIFE ACC MEN'S TOURNAMENT - QUARTERFINAL

videos.description: Louisville's defense triggers a fastbreak that Deng Adel finishes with a ferocious one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Adel throws down one-handed jam

videos.description: Duke's Luke Kennard misses a jumper, collects his own rebound, then gets fouled on the made second chance shot.
videos.headline: Kennard gets own rebound and hits jumper and-1

videos.description: Duke's Jayson Tatum pump fakes one defender and splits two more as he hits an acrobatic layup.
videos.headline: Tatum goes by three defenders on his way to a layup

videos.description: Louisville head coach Rick Pitino discusses his thoughts on the 1st half officiating and the offensive success that his team had.
videos.headline: Pitino on 1st half foul calls

videos.description: Duke's Jayson Tatum finishes a fastbreak with a one-handed slam.
videos.headline: Tatum throws down fastbreak dunk

videos.description: Duke's Luke Kennard makes a 3-pointer to tie the game against Louisville.
videos.headline: Kennard knocks down a three to tie game

videos.description: Louisville's Deng Adel is fouled as he makes a tough layup in the lane.
videos.headline: Cardinals answer with tough layup and-1

videos.description: Duke's Luke Kennard drains another 3-pointer to give Duke a 73-70 lead with under five minutes to play.
videos.headline: Kennard hits another big 3-pointer for Duke

videos.description: Jayson Tatum puts Duke up by five with a corner 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Tatum hits late three

videos.description: Louisville's Mangok Mathiang rejects Luke Kennard in the paint and Quentin Snider is fouled at the other end.
videos.headline: Huge block leads to Louisville free throws

videos.description: Duke head coach Mike Krzyzewski talks about his team's second half performance against Louisville and his thoughts on playing North Carolina on Friday.
videos.headline: Krzyzewski on Duke's late win over Louisville

videos.description: Breaking down North Carolina's victory over Miami and Duke's win against Louisville.
videos.headline: Postgame Breakdown of Miami vs. North Carolina and Duke vs. Louisville

videos.description: Jayson Tatum and Luke Kennard combine for 49 points as Louisville fails to connect on a game-tying three and Duke advances to face North Carolina in the ACC semifinals.
videos.headline: Duke fends off Louisville, will face UNC
